img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁多間真係喜來稀肉最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其熟食"},{"pid":"84320792b11f2aa4d9c2da16376ff1e8695e3bb9","tid":395053,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"好撚難食"},{"pid":"4b211ccf65e7f2badc8ba23a5734668b8c3eb6cf","tid":395053,"uid":97250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"前幾日食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b831a5ac55965612e1d0f53128c23084f92f16e","tid":395053,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識食一定係食喜來稀肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁多間真係喜來稀肉最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其熟食</blockquote><br />\n嗚啊聽到個名都肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c60b5c124126b5142237ad7be5e06d47365c79c","tid":395053,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T22:12:52.000Z","msg":"個桃冰又真係唔錯<br />\n有成兩個白桃<br />\n仲有桃嘅糖漿<br />\n係initial 個隻香水味，我同條女都鐘意，所以覺得勁正<br />\n<br />\n唯一唔好就係d 冰，多碎冰，好快溶哂成碗水"},{"pid":"fb45226c9dbb42f2b0f3e63cda6782c618e16774","tid":395053,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識食一定係食喜來稀肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁多間真係喜來稀肉最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其熟食</blockquote><br />\n嗚啊聽到個名都肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲肉擺係後巷坑渠側邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔敢再去呢間<br />\n實有人話其他都係咁 不過我睇唔到起碼安心少少先<br />\n<br />\nbtw上星期食左炑八 個桃冰等勁耐 起碼半個鐘至九個字 但都幾好食 韓燒方面無咩comment都係普通 有得refill蛋同芝士"},{"pid":"ca72ae05d90ec0a77b1a744ecd05d44c4163ac7f","tid":395053,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"韓式燒肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f3949266bd842f85952c3124ba82dda201eea0","tid":395053,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"LUNCH 一人燒肉都幾抵"},{"pid":"3cb8360b491bf8b8f945bae9b5c11e6c351aef83","tid":395053,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識食一定係食喜來稀肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁多間真係喜來稀肉最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其熟食</blockquote><br />\n笑撚左<br />\n利申:做過"},{"pid":"bc937ce4fbe40014b2ed7a07058ef88d3a200fc8","tid":395053,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77330d62dd6204ee44e7df51c95ab052f651489c","tid":395053,"uid":81211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"我唔鐘意食韓國野，但佢個下午茶性價比真係沒得輸<br />\n48蚊一個餐送例湯，無限任添野飲，無限任添芽菜，泡菜。<br />\n<br />\n仲要任坐，沒人趕你走"},{"pid":"9ce5beefb727a6b81efcbbfe916c19bff8384bae","tid":395053,"uid":1707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一啲都唔抵 野食係幾好味 但絕對唔值咁貴"},{"pid":"c7d9510188b3dba8319cebcb3fb05ad4d7eee6c7","tid":395053,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}